title: Rolling Stones - Fast Talking
description:
The Rolling Stones - Fast Talking 

Studio outtakes, mostly instrumentals. Recorded at Musicland Studios (Germany, 1973 & 1974), Dynamic Sound Studios (Jamaica, 1972), Electra Studios (Los Angeles, 1972), Pathe Marconi Studios (Paris, 1978), Compass Point Studio (Nassau, 1979).
